		</varlistentry>

		<varlistentry>
			<term><synopsis>Compatibility</synopsis></term>
			<listitem><para>
				mod_ldap v2.8.11 and later
			</para></listitem>
		</varlistentry>
	</variablelist>
</refsynopsisdiv>

	<refsect1>
		<title>Description</title>

		<para>This configuration directive activates LDAP quota lookups. 
		The second argument to this directive is the LDAP prefix to use for
		quota limit search.  The third argument is a template to be used for
		the search filter; %v will be replaced with the username that is
		being authenticated. By default, the search filter template
		"(&amp;(uid=%v)(objectclass=posixAccount))" is used. Search filter
		templates are only supported in mod_ldap v2.7 and later.</para>
	</refsect1>

